red’ population: in the first century after the Conquest it was the commonest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Whitby was born in 1500. He had at least 1 son with Francis William. He died in 1560, at the age of 60."},"et":{"1500–1560":"1500–1560","1505–Female":"1505–Surnud","1535–Male":"1535–Surnud","1535":"1535","1500":"1500","about 1535":"umbes 1535","1560":"1560","1505":"1505","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, England"},"fi":{"1500–1560":"1500–1560","1505–Female":"1505–Kuollut","1535–Male":"1535–Kuollut","1535":"1535","1500":"1500","about 1535":"noin 1535","1560":"1560","1505":"1505","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, England"},"fr":{"1500–1560":"1500–1560","1505–Female":"1505–Décédée","1535–Male":"1535–Décédé","1535":"1535","1500":"1500","about 1535":"environ 1535","1560":"1560","1505":"1505","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"William Whitby est né en 1500. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Francis William. Il est décédé en 1560, à l’âge de 60 ans."},"de":{"1500–1560":"1500–1560","1505–Female":"1505–Verstorben","1535–Male":"1535–Verstorben","1535":"1535","1500":"1500","about 1535":"um 1535","1560":"1560","1505":"1505","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, England","lifeSummary":"William Whitby wurde 1500 geboren. Er hatte mit Francis William mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1560 im Alter von 60 Jahren."},"ht":{"1500–1560":"1500–1560","1505–Female":"1505–Desede","1535–Male":"1535–Desede","1535":"1535","1500":"1500","about 1535":"about 1535","1560":"1560","1505":"1505","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, England"},"hu":{"1500–1560":"1500–1560","1505–Female":"1505–elhunyt","1535–Male":"1535–elhunyt","1535":"1